lyrics:
[verse]
In the depths of despair, where darkness prevails
Dickfoot emerges, without a voice to wail
Haunted melodies resonate, a silent cry
No singer remains, as time passes us by

[chorus]
Dickfoot's lament echoes through the gloom
Guitar riffs weep, in the depths of their tomb
Drums pound like thunder, setting the pace
An instrumental dirge for the fallen grace
